extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value:
The Duelist Genesis set is the first to feature cards from the all-new Yugioh! 5D's animated series. The Duelist Genesis set introduces new types of monsters and a new game mechanic. Included are the new Psychic-Type monsters and Synchro Monsters with Tuners (effect monsters that fuse with regular monsters to bring out Synchro monsters).
Set Configuration
The 100-card set (48 commons, 20 rares, 12 super rares, and 10 ultra rares) includes 10 cards exclusive to Upper Deck and 10 cards previously only released in Japan!
